OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780413074
OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FAdditional reporting by Washington
OL,7,FProducer Joshua Brooks
OL,9,FThe US city of Boston is now in the
OL,10,Ffinal countdown for this summer's FIFA
OL,11,FWorld Cup, as the city prepares to
OL,12,Fwelcome thousands of fans, including
OL,13,Fmany from England and Scotland.
OL,15,FSecurity is a paramount concern in a
OL,16,Fcity which contended with the Boston
OL,17,FMarathon bombings 13 years ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
