OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780413074
OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FThe operation at Boston's stadium, in
OL,7,Fthe nearby town of Foxborough, will be
OL,8,Foverseen by local police, led by their
OL,9,FChief Michael Grace.
OL,11,FWhen I asked him about the perception
OL,12,Fof American law enforcement, after
OL,13,Frecent controversial incidents
OL,14,Finvolving fatal shootings in
OL,15,FMinneapolis during an Immigration and
OL,16,FCustom Enforcement crackdown, he was
OL,17,Frobust in his defence of Boston's
OL,18,Fpolicing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
