PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780413074
OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FHe insisted its reputation was
OL,7,Fundiminished, telling me: "I would
OL,8,Fdisagree 100 % that what you see in
OL,9,Fthese protests is policing is in
OL,10,FAmerica, and that is not what they
OL,11,Fwill expect when they arrive in fan-
OL,12,Ffest or even when they land at Logan
OL,13,Fairport.
OL,15,F"They'll see police there being
OL,16,Fprofessional very approachable at all
OL,17,Ftimes."
OL,19,FWe were given exclusive access to
OL,20,Ftheir SWAT teams, as they trained at
OL,21,Fthe stadium.
OL,26,@oD@[OUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
