OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FFrom hostage rescue to storming
OL,7,Fhostile vehicles, they must be
OL,8,Fprepared to respond to anything.
OL,10,FMany of those we watched being put
OL,11,Fthrough their paces, helped to respond
OL,12,Fto the terror attacks in 2013.
OL,14,FThe shadow of that incident looms
OL,15,Flarge over their training.
OL,17,FThey will be among the first to
OL,18,Frespond, and this is one of their last
OL,19,Fchances to prepare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
