OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FAll are armed with assault rifles and
OL,7,Fpistols.
OL,9,FThey also have an armoured Bearcat
OL,10,Fvehicle, similar to a military MRAP
OL,11,Fpersonnel carrier at their disposal in
OL,12,Fcase their need to storm a house or
OL,13,Fvehicle.
OL,15,FThey are leaving nothing to chance
OL,16,Fthis summer.
OL,18,FWe watched as they practised storming
OL,19,Fthe executive suites of the stadium,
OL,20,Fensuring their communication is clear
OL,21,Fand their tactics are agreed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
