OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780413074
OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FThey know the eyes of the world will
OL,7,Fbe on them as the tournament gets
OL,8,Funderway, with five group stage
OL,9,Fmatches, plus a group of 32 game and a
OL,10,Fquarter final.
OL,12,FBoston might be famous for its rich
OL,13,FIrish heritage, but this summer it is
OL,14,Fthe English and Scottish who will
OL,15,Fflood the Massachusetts city, with at
OL,16,Fleast two Scotland games (against
OL,17,FHaiti on 13th June and 6 days later
OL,18,Fagainst Morocco) and one England game
OL,19,F(on 23 June against Ghana).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
