OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780413074
OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FPreparations are already well under
OL,7,Fway, with an outdoor fan zone in the
OL,8,Fcentre ready for the thousands of
OL,9,Fvisitors.
OL,11,FHowever, the logistics for those
OL,12,Ftravelling here for the matches will
OL,13,Fnot be straightforward.
OL,15,FThe stadium (normally called the
OL,16,FGillette Stadium where the New England
OL,17,FPatriots American Football team play)
OL,18,Fis an hour away by car to the south.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
