OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780413074
OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FEven on quiet days the traffic can be
OL,7,Ftricky, but during the tournament
OL,8,Fthere are concerns the highway there
OL,9,Fwill be jammed solid as almost 80,000
OL,10,Ffans descend on the venue.
OL,12,FThere is a train, but unlike at many
OL,13,Fprevious World Cup events, here the
OL,14,Fpublic transport is not free.
OL,16,FInstead will cost $95 US dollars
OL,17,F(about #70) for a return journey.
OL,19,FMike Loynds FIFA's local organising
OL,20,Fcommittee in Boston defended the
OL,21,Fcharge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
