OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780413074
OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,F"It's well below the cost price, and
OL,7,Fso we're comfortable with those
OL,8,Fprices, and the experience we are
OL,9,Fgoing to provide the fans," he said.
OL,11,FStill it has raised eyebrows given the
OL,12,Fcost of match tickets will run into
OL,13,Fthe hundreds or thousands of dollars.
OL,15,FOne enterprising local businessman is
OL,16,Foffering a closer option, at his Haven
OL,17,FBar, the only Scottish themed pub in
OL,18,Fthe city.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
