OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FJason Waddleton says 400 kegs of
OL,7,FScottish lager have been ordered for
OL,8,Fthe city, 150 of which are destined
OL,9,Ffor his venue.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FDeep fried Mars bars will be on the
OL,17,FScottish themed menu as he prepares to
OL,18,Fwelcome the Tartan Army.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
