OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FThe buzz is beginning to build across
OL,7,Fthe city, even if many American's are
OL,8,Fonly dimly aware of the 'soccer'
OL,9,Ffestival about to get underway in
OL,10,Ftheir midst.
OL,12,FA city which celebrates its Boston tea
OL,13,Fparty rebellion, against British taxes
OL,14,Flevied in the name of King George III,
OL,15,Fis now ready to welcome back the
OL,16,FEnglish and Scottish.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
