OL,3,CHow is Boston preparing to host
OL,4,CEngland and Scotland at the World Cup?
OL,6,FHowever, it's likely that beer, not
OL,7,Ftea, will be the preferred
OL,8,Frefreshment, as the fans cheer on
OL,9,Ftheir teams to get through the group
OL,10,Fstage and into the final stage of the
OL,11,FWorld Cup.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
